item.description:
@Ruby_Forums_Coder wrote:

[quote=“kidgoku4522, post:21, topic:466082”][quote author=Ruby link=topic=575661.msg4149957#msg4149957 date=1352389011]
Everyone blame Whackatre for putting these customs out there the butthole that he is.
[/quote]
LoL shit customs at that >.>
No one likes em I had 2 people who loved customs on my old server and they were 11 year olds i was like -_- This server gonna be shit shutting it down
prob what he did…
lol[/quote]

When Whackatre was running Project Rainbow he had over 100 online at one point and was the number one delta server nevermind the number one custom server. When I was his website developer the average age was more or less the same as any other server, 11-16 usually.

He only closed it down because he had outgrown RSPS programming. He still has a programming community if you look at SkyRealm
